{
  "texts": [
    "Miotto et al. (2018) proposed a novel framework to integrate and analyse heterogeneous health data using deep learning.",
    "They showed how AI can extract meaningful insights and patterns from complex and diverse data sources, such as electronic health records, genomic data, and clinical notes.",
    "This study shows how AI can enable personalised and precision medicine and improve public health research.",
    "Shi et al. (2017) introduced AI into the realm of weather forecasting, introducing the LSTM (long short-term memory) model.",
    "This model, which is capable of capturing spatio-temporal correlations in precipitation data, outperformed traditional models."
  ]
}